From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 1 Dec 2025 16:14:37 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] drm/panthor: Sky1 G720 support with debug instrumentation

Work-in-progress Sky1/G720 support including:
- HOST_POWER register definitions for G720 (arch >= 12)
- Sky1-specific power sequence (legacy SHADER_PWRON path)
- Pre-power shaders before MCU boot
- MCU configuration with poweroff_timer=0, core_en_mask
- G720 CSF interface changes (endpoint_req_hi)
- Sky1 MMU flush workaround
- PM domain and reset controller handling
- Q-channel clock gating via RCSU

Contains debug instrumentation to be cleaned up.
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6.dts |   4 +-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_device.c  |  52 ++++-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_fw.c      | 122 ++++++++++-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_fw.h      |  13 +-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_gpu.c     | 238 +++++++++++++++++++++-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_gpu.h     |   1 +
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_mmu.c     |  34 +++-
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_regs.h    |  34 ++++
 drivers/gpu/drm/panthor/panthor_sched.c   |  89 +++++++-
 9 files changed, 560 insertions(+), 27 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6.dts
